data.description: This custom Victorian Farmhouse built by CL Design-Build with open floor plan has ship lap ceiling in Kitchen, coffered ceiling in Great Room, crown moulding, 5 panel doors, white oak floors, custom built-in surround fireplace, wet bar, gourmet kitchen with old fashioned stove & 2 islands! Study/Guest BR w/full bath on main floor, custom stairs to 3rd level attic. Vaulted turret in Master BR w/dressing room featuring 2nd laundry, 2 WIC, Master Bath has claw foot tub. Finished Bsmt w/"English Pub" Bar, Rec Rm, Exercise Rm./Bedroom, full Bath, Media Rm w/theater seating, and entrance from garage. Finished Bonus Rm/Office over garage. Outdoor w/built-in grill and full fireplace. Brick paver courtyard and walk. Certainteed 100 yr dbl laminated asphalt roof, fibercement siding.
data.whatILove: Lots of built-ins. The 4117 sf includes finished office in Bonus Room over garage. Professionally landscaped with mature trees. Built-in grill and fireplace at concrete patio. Paver courtyard with sidewalk to front door and a wrap around front porch. 9ft ceiling at 1st floor. Coffered ceiling in Great Room.
